製圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20250619/1012401047714795520138426.jpeg/1MnTgSWuQLNnMgqB1wdTUJnbyevHJ6U4VjCVwlYwlcI\" alt=\"工作太依賴AI，思考習慣也會改變？（01製圖）\"><figcaption>工作太依賴AI，思考習慣也會改變？（01製圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20250619/1012401049900158976731842.jpeg/LNsFW3jMvNfVz2NVeSZv73IYX651-QAFmAlxJpgJcSY\" alt=\"工作太依賴AI，思考習慣也會改變？（01製圖）\"><figcaption>工作太依賴AI，思考習慣也會改變？（01製圖）</figcaption></figure><p>延伸閲讀：</p><p>擁1.2億退休資產！工程師1原因長年裝沒錢 真相曝光全家氣炸</p><p>資產逾3千萬！二寶媽靠副業「被動收入月賺44萬」2招翻身成富翁</p><p>【本文獲「聯合新聞網」授權轉載。】</p></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-24T05:10:13.617866+00:00","quality":{"score":3,"chars":3131,"images":63,"source":"HK01 國際","fallback":"none"}}